# 🔍 Metasploit Methodology Engine (MME) Report

**Generated on:** <%= Time.now.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S') %>
**Target:** <%= metadata[:target] %>
**Tool Version:** v<%= metadata[:tool_version] %>
**Duration:** <%= metadata[:duration] %> seconds

---

## 📊 Executive Summary

**Total Attack Surface:**
- Hosts Scanned: <%= metadata[:hosts_scanned] %>
- Services Discovered: <%= metadata[:services_found] %>

**Findings Summary (<%= sorted_findings.size %> Total):**
<% Finding::SEVERITIES.each do |sev| %>
- **<%= sev.capitalize %>**: <%= severity_summary[sev] || 0 %>
<% end %>

---

## 🛑 Top Findings (Highest Severity)

<% top_findings = sorted_findings.select { |f| %w[critical high].include?(f.severity.to_s.downcase) }.take(5) %>
<% if top_findings.empty? %>
*No Critical or High severity findings discovered.*
<% else %>
<% top_findings.each do |f| %>
### [<%= f.severity.upcase %>] <%= f.title %>
- **Host:** <%= f.host %>:<%= f.port %> (<%= f.service.upcase %>)
- **Module:** `<%= f.module_path %>`
- **Impact:** <%= f.impact.empty? ? 'N/A' : f.impact %>
- **Remediation:** <%= f.remediation.empty? ? 'N/A' : f.remediation %>
<% if f.exploits && f.exploits.any? %>
- **Available Exploits:**
<% f.exploits.each do |exp| %>
  - `use <%= exp[:fullname] %>` (Confidence: <%= exp[:confidence] || 'Possible' %>)
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

---

## 📋 Detailed Findings by Host

<% if findings_by_host.empty? %>
*No findings were discovered during this execution.*
<% else %>
<% findings_by_host.each do |host, host_findings| %>
### Host: <%= host %>
*(<%= host_findings.size %> Findings)*

<% host_findings.each do |f| %>
#### [<%= f.severity.upcase %>] <%= f.title %>
**Service:** <%= f.service.upcase %> (Port <%= f.port %>)
**Module:** `<%= f.module_path %>`
**Status:** <%= f.status.capitalize %>

**Description:**
<%= f.description %>

<% if f.evidence && f.evidence.any? %>
**Evidence:**
```text
<% f.evidence.each do |ev| %>
<%= ev.to_s.lines.reject { |l| l.strip.empty? || l.match?(/Scanned \d+ of \d+ hosts|New in Metasploit/) }.map { |l| l.sub(/^\[\+\]\s+/, '').sub(/^\[\*\]\s+/, '').sub(/^\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+:\d+\s+-\s+/, '').strip }.reject(&:empty?).join("\n") %>
<% end %>
```
<% end %>

---
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>
